it.csi.mddtools.appresources
Interface ServiceConnector

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, ResourceConnector
All Known Subinterfaces:
PDPAServiceConnector, RPCWebServiceConnector
public interface ServiceConnector
extends ResourceConnector

A representation of the model object 'Service Connector'. Connettore (astratto) per risorse di tipo "servizio"

The following features are supported:

  • Service Def
  • Binding
  • Selector
  • Use Registry

See Also:
